{
  "texts": [
    "You can choose the same mountain chosen by other participants or a different mountain.",
    "At the end of Stage 1, the gems hidden in each mountain selected by all participants in Stage 1 are revealed, and you earn the value of the gem hidden in the mountain you chose.",
    "In Stage 2, you can again choose any of the same {len(MOUNTAINS_DISTRIBUTION)} mountains; that is, you can either choose the same mountain of Stage 1 or switch to another one.",
    "The position of gems remains the same as in Stage 1, but this time you will also see the gems located in the mountains revealed in Stage 1 in addition to the mapped mountain.",
    "At the end of Stage 2, the gems hidden in each mountain selected by all participants in Stage 2 are revealed, and you earn the value of the gem hidden in the mountain you chose in Stage 2."
  ]
}